sequenceDiagram
  participant Installer
  participant API
  participant Verifier
  participant VerifSvc
  participant Ledger
  participant Split
  participant Wallet

  Installer->>API: mark project installed + upload evidence images
  API->>VerifSvc: create verification task
  Verifier->>API: submit verification (photos, notes)
  API->>Ledger: write verification hash (immutable proof)
  Ledger-->>API: hash_id
  API->>DB: mark verification record with hash, status=approved
  API->>Split: trigger final settlement for any pending splits (transfer or wallet credit)
  Split->>Wallet: disburse funds
  Wallet->>DB: create transaction records
  API-->>Installer: notify payout
